  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Moore\" title=\"House Moore\"><img alt=\"House Moore.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/33/House_Moore.svg/50px-House_Moore.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/33/House_Moore.svg/75px-House_Moore.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/33/House_Moore.svg/100px-House_Moore.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Lady</span><br />Perianne Moore</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Mooton\" title=\"House Mooton\"><img alt=\"House Mooton.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/a6/House_Mooton.svg/50px-House_Mooton.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/a6/House_Mooton.svg/75px-House_Mooton.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/a6/House_Mooton.svg/100px-House_Mooton.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Saera_targaryen%27s_Pretty_Peri_by_viscardiac.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Saera targaryen&#39;s Pretty Peri by viscardiac.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/ce/Saera_targaryen%27s_Pretty_Peri_by_viscardiac.png/350px-Saera_targaryen%27s_Pretty_Peri_by_viscardiac.png\" width=\"350\" height=\"467\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/ce/Saera_targaryen%27s_Pretty_Peri_by_viscardiac.png/525px-Saera_targaryen%27s_Pretty_Peri_by_viscardiac.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/ce/Saera_targaryen%27s_Pretty_Peri_by_viscardiac.png/700px-Saera_targaryen%27s_Pretty_Peri_by_viscardiac.png 2x\" /></a><div>Perianne Moore, by <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://viscardiac.tumblr.com/\">viscardiac</a></div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Alias</th><td>\nPretty Peri<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\nLady of <a href=\"/index.php/Maidenpool\" title=\"Maidenpool\">Maidenpool</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiances</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Moore\" title=\"House Moore\">House Moore</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Mooton\" title=\"House Mooton\">House Mooton</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Valemen\" title=\"Valemen\">Valemen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_67_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">67&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Spouse</th><td>\nLord <a href=\"/index.php/Jonah_Mooton\" title=\"Jonah Mooton\">Jonah Mooton</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Rise_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"The Rise of the Dragon\">The Rise of the Dragon</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Perianne Moore</b> was a member of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Moore\" title=\"House Moore\">House Moore</a> during the reign of King <a href=\"/index.php/Jaehaerys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Jaehaerys I Targaryen\">Jaehaerys I Targaryen</a> and a <a href=\"/index.php/Lady_companion\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Lady companion\">lady companion</a> to Jaehaerys's daughter, Princess <a href=\"/index.php/Saera_Targaryen\" title=\"Saera Targaryen\">Saera Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Appearance_and_Character\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Appearance and Character</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance_and_Character\">Appearance and Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Perianne_Moore&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearance and Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Alysanne_Targaryen\" title=\"Alysanne Targaryen\">Alysanne Targaryen</a> considered Lady Perianne to be a pretty, vapid, empty-headed little fool from what she had seen of her. <a href=\"/index.php/Grand_Maester\" title=\"Grand Maester\">Grand Maester</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Elysar\" title=\"Elysar\">Elysar</a> called her a <a href=\"http://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/trull\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"wikt:trull\">trull</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Perianne_Moore&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Perianne was a <a href=\"/index.php/Maiden\" title=\"Maiden\">maiden</a> of an age with Princess <a href=\"/index.php/Saera_Targaryen\" title=\"Saera Targaryen\">Saera Targaryen</a>, attending the royal court at the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_Keep\" title=\"Red Keep\">Red Keep</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a>. In <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_82_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">82&#160;AC</a>, Perianne became a favorite and dearest friend of the princess, along with <a href=\"/index.php/Alys_Turnberry\" title=\"Alys Turnberry\">Alys Turnberry</a>.  Saera nicknamed Perianne <i>\"Pretty Peri\".</i><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Saera and her five favorites — Perianne, Alys, <a href=\"/index.php/Jonah_Mooton\" title=\"Jonah Mooton\">Jonah Mooton</a>, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Roy_Connington\" title=\"Roy Connington\">Roy Connington</a>, and Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Braxton_Beesbury\" title=\"Braxton Beesbury\">Braxton Beesbury</a>, called Stinger — became inseparable at every feast and ball. They hunted and <a href=\"/index.php/Hawk\" title=\"Hawk\">hawked</a> together, and once sailed across <a href=\"/index.php/Blackwater_Bay\" title=\"Blackwater Bay\">Blackwater Bay</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Dragonstone\" title=\"Dragonstone\">Dragonstone</a> together. When the young lords <a href=\"/index.php/Ride_at_rings\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Ride at rings\">rode at rings</a> or crossed swords in the yards, the three girls cheered them on. King <a href=\"/index.php/Jaehaerys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Jaehaerys I Targaryen\">Jaehaerys I Targaryen</a> was pleased at his daughter's popularity and friendship, but Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Alysanne_Targaryen\" title=\"Alysanne Targaryen\">Alysanne Targaryen</a> was concerned about the character of Perianne, Alys, and the three boys. Nevertheless, King Jaehaerys felt they could not get up to trouble, with all the servants attending them watching.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> \n</p><p>In <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_84_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">84&#160;AC</a>, an incident occurred between Saera's male favorites and <a href=\"/index.php/Tom_Turnip\" title=\"Tom Turnip\">Tom Turnip</a>, King Jaehaerys's <a href=\"/index.php/Fool\" title=\"Fool\">fool</a>, at the <a href=\"/index.php/Blue_Pearl\" title=\"Blue Pearl\">Blue Pearl</a>, a <a href=\"/index.php/Brothel\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Brothel\">brothel</a> in King's Landing, something Jonah claimed had been the princess's idea. Perianne and Alys were woken in the middle of the night and questioned by Queen Alysanne, telling them to tell the truth or they would join their male friends in the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_Keep#Dungeon\" title=\"Red Keep\">dungeons</a>. Before long, the girls were weeping and pleading for forgiveness, although their confessions said almost nothing about the incident they were being questioned about. Perianne explained that Saera had been teaching Alys how to kiss, and she asked to be taught to kiss too, to train for their future marriages. Alys revealed that one night the girls had started kissing each other with their clothes off, taking turns pretending they were boys. Then, Saera dared Alys to kiss a real boy, and she dared Perianne, and both dared Saera, who said she would kiss a man grown, a <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a>. This began the ladies' affairs with Red Roy, Jonah, and Stinger. Perianne explained that Stinger did the \"training\" for all of them.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Queen Alysanne then demanded to know where their <a href=\"/index.php/Septa\" title=\"Septa\">septas</a> and servants had been during all of this. Perianne, confused, explained that servants do what you tell them, and they had sent them out of the room. As for the ones who knew, Stinger had threatened to <a href=\"/index.php/Tongue_mutilation\" title=\"Tongue mutilation\">have their tongues out</a> if they talked. Alys then confessed to being with child, and that she did not know who the father was. Alysanne sent both girls to bed, and told them that the next morning they would make a confession to a septa and be forgiven by <a href=\"/index.php/Mother_(the_Seven)\" title=\"Mother (the Seven)\">the Mother</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-8\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Hasty <a href=\"/index.php/Marriage\" title=\"Marriage\">marriages</a> were arranged for the two girls. Perianne, who was not pregnant, was wed to another of Saera's favorites, Jonah Mooton, the heir to <a href=\"/index.php/Maidenpool\" title=\"Maidenpool\">Maidenpool</a>. The king told Jonah that since he had played a part in Perianne's ruin, he should play a part in her redemption. The marriage was successful, and eventually Jonah and Perianne ruled together as Lord and Lady of Maidenpool.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-9\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>A year and a half after the scandal, Saera fled from her punishment in <a href=\"/index.php/Oldtown\" title=\"Oldtown\">Oldtown</a>. King Jaehaerys thought she might seek out her friends, and told Jonah and Perianne to keep watch for her in Maidenpool, but Saera did not go there.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-10\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Perianne_Moore&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>The boys train at fighting every morning, why shouldn't we train at kissing? That's what girls are meant to do, isn't it?<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-11\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;Perianne, to Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Alysanne_Targaryen\" title=\"Alysanne Targaryen\">Alysanne Targaryen</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><a href=\"/index.php/Saera_Targaryen\" title=\"Saera Targaryen\">Saera</a> is smarter than the <a href=\"/index.php/Septa\" title=\"Septa\">septas</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-12\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;Perianne, to Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Alysanne_Targaryen\" title=\"Alysanne Targaryen\">Alysanne Targaryen</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Perianne_Moore&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.00</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.01</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.02</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\">1.03</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\">1.04</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-5\">1.05</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-6\">1.06</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-7\">1.07</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-8\">1.08</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-9\">1.09</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-10\">1.10</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-11\">1.11</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-12\">1.12</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, The Long Reign - Jaehaerys and Alysanne: Policy, Progeny, and Pain.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i>See the <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest/Calculations_Ages_(Continued2)#Perianne_Moore\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest/Calculations Ages (Continued2)\">Perianne Moore</a> calculation.</i></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403142510\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.106 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.315 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 1495/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 11073/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 14215/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1734/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 12/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 4009/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.190/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.57 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  296.289      1 -total\n 89.56%  265.368      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 89.04%  263.821      1 Template:Infobo